column5: Hey all, does anyone have any group photos from last years Fishing forTyler?  I went through my folder and it seems I didn't have a chance to take that many pictures, don't know why   and the ones I did take or have copies of are not groups just individual shots for the most part.  Thanks Maureen
Maureen,  I have smaller groups of 3 or 4....but I dont recall a big group shot being taken.  Let me know if you'd like some of those pics.  Cliff
I just looked and all I have are groups of two.
Here are some shots from last year....

Thanks Cliff, that last one is great!  I'll likely forward it to a reporter at the Barrie Examiner if it's ok with you...maybe shoot me a PM with your full name and permission to use it so I can make sure you get credit for it if he uses it,  Maureen
Here's a few with prizes and stuff, but sorry, I have no group shot either.         Joey
